cloud-architecture-diagram
direction right
colorMode pastel
styleMode shadow
typeface clean

User [color: "#F7F3E8"]

FE [color: "#E9F5DB"] {
  OperationsPages [label: "configuration.html / auto.html / iot.html"]
  DashboardJS [label: "dashboard.js\nVanilla JS chat/STT/TTS client"]
  SampleUI [label: "server_api/src/modules/llm/sample\nindex.html + static/js/index.js"]
}

BE [color: "#DCEBFF"] {
  MainPy [label: "src/main.py\nFastAPI app entry"]
  ApiV1 [label: "src/api/v1/router.py"]
  LlmRouter [label: "src/modules/llm/router.py\n/api/v1/llm"]
  ChatAPI [label: "llm_chat_api.py\n/chat, /memory, /knowledge, /upload"]
  MediaAPI [label: "llm_media_api.py\n/stt, /tts, /image"]
  QuestionAPI [label: "llm_question.py\n/recommended-questions"]
  ResultAPI [label: "llm_result_api.py\n/result"]
}

Domain [color: "#FFF2CC"] {
  KnowledgeService [label: "knowledge_service.py\nloading + OCR + indexing"]
  AgentService [label: "agent_service.py\nget_agent()"]
  CSAgent [label: "sample/agent.py\nCSAgent orchestration"]
  OpenAIService [label: "openai_service.py\nOpenAI client factory"]
  EnvConfig [label: "env_loader.py + settings.py\n.env + app settings"]
}

External [color: "#FDE2E4"] {
  OpenAIChat [label: "OpenAI Chat\n(gpt-4o-mini)"]
  OpenAIAudio [label: "OpenAI Audio\nSTT / TTS"]
  OpenAIImage [label: "OpenAI Images\n(gpt-image-1 / dall-e-3)"]
  OpenAIVision [label: "OpenAI Vision OCR\n(gpt-4.1-mini)"]
  Serper [label: "Serper search API"]
  Tavily [label: "Tavily search API"]
  Vllm [label: "vLLM endpoint\n(optional)"]
  Gemini [label: "Google Gemini\n(optional)"]
}

Data [color: "#E8DFF5"] {
  KnowledgeFolder [label: "LLM_KNOWLEDGE_PATH\nTXT / PDF / Image files"]
  FaissRetriever [label: "In-memory FAISS retriever\noptional"]
  SessionState [label: "In-memory session state\nchat_history / memory_summary /\nknowledge_memory / web_history"]
  MemoryCaches [label: "In-memory caches\n_web_cache / _answer_cache /\n_llm_cache / _client_cache"]
  Postgres [label: "PostgreSQL app DB\nuser_table / vector_table /\nface_embedding_table / items"]
}

Notes [color: "#F3F4F6"] {
  NoDirectLlmDb [label: "LLM module has no direct SQLAlchemy CRUD path"]
  SampleScope [label: "sample/ is demo UI, separate from nginx operations UI"]
}

User > OperationsPages: uses
User > SampleUI: uses demo

OperationsPages > DashboardJS: binds events
DashboardJS > LlmRouter: calls /api/v1/llm/*
SampleUI > ChatAPI: calls /api/chat
SampleUI > MediaAPI: calls /api/stt /api/tts /api/image

MainPy > ApiV1: includes
ApiV1 > LlmRouter: registers
MainPy > Postgres: create_all on startup

LlmRouter > ChatAPI: routes
LlmRouter > MediaAPI: routes
LlmRouter > QuestionAPI: routes
LlmRouter > ResultAPI: routes

ChatAPI > KnowledgeService: ensure knowledge / upload / reindex
ChatAPI > AgentService: get singleton
ChatAPI > CSAgent: stream answer
ChatAPI > SessionState: read/write memory
ChatAPI > KnowledgeFolder: save uploads

KnowledgeService > KnowledgeFolder: read files
KnowledgeService > OpenAIVision: OCR image files
KnowledgeService > FaissRetriever: build retriever
KnowledgeService > CSAgent: inject local docs

AgentService > CSAgent: returns singleton
CSAgent > SessionState: store chat turns
CSAgent > MemoryCaches: cache web and answers
CSAgent > FaissRetriever: retrieve context
CSAgent > Serper: search fresh web facts
CSAgent > Tavily: search fresh web facts
CSAgent > OpenAIChat: send prompt / receive stream
CSAgent > Vllm: optional provider
CSAgent > Gemini: optional provider

QuestionAPI > OpenAIService: get client
QuestionAPI > OpenAIChat: generate question list

ResultAPI > OpenAIService: get client
ResultAPI > OpenAIChat: single prompt completion

MediaAPI > OpenAIService: get client
MediaAPI > OpenAIAudio: STT / TTS
MediaAPI > OpenAIImage: image generation

OpenAIService > EnvConfig: read env
EnvConfig > OpenAIChat: configure API key

NoDirectLlmDb > Postgres: boundary
SampleScope > SampleUI: scope
